# Technology Stack

This project uses the following technologies and frameworks:

## Core Technologies

- [Astro](mdc:https:/astro.build) - The web framework for content-driven websites
- [Storyblok](mdc:https:/www.storyblok.com) - Headless CMS for content management
- [React](mdc:https:/reactjs.org) - Library for interactive UI components
- [TypeScript](mdc:https:/www.typescriptlang.org) - Type-safe JavaScript

## UI and Styling

- [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com) - Utility-first CSS framework
- [Radix UI](mdc:https:/www.radix-ui.com) - Unstyled, accessible UI components
- [Lucide](mdc:https:/lucide.dev) - Icon library
- [Embla Carousel](mdc:https:/www.embla-carousel.com) - Carousel/slider library

## Development Tools

- [Prettier](mdc:https:/prettier.io) - Code formatter
- [Vite](mdc:https:/vitejs.dev) - Build tool and development server
- [Node.js](mdc:https:/nodejs.org) - JavaScript runtime for SSR mode

## Deployment

- [Docker](mdc:https:/www.docker.com) - Containerization platform
- [Nginx](mdc:https:/nginx.org) - Web server for static deployments
